  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8256597">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8256597/" class="title-link">最高效的政治机器</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8256597"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1679535-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">维舟</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-12-27"
      class="main-meta">2016-12-27 14:06:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8256597_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  伟大的思想往往都是含混甚至潜藏着内在矛盾的。这一点，在马克斯·韦伯这位“资产阶级的马克思”身上似乎再度得到了印证。在世人的印象中，这位曾提出现代资本主义奠基于新教伦理的社会学家自己就是一个冷峻的清教徒，很多人不由自主地把他所提出的“学术的价值中立”等命题看...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8256597/#comments">(11回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">74有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8256597_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8256597_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
